org.deeplearning4j.models.sequencevectors

Class SequenceVectors<T extends SequenceElement>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.deeplearning4j.models.embeddings.wordvectors.WordVectorsImpl<T>
      • org.deeplearning4j.models.sequencevectors.SequenceVectors<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, WordVectors
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Glove, Node2Vec, SparkSequenceVectors, Word2Vec

    public class SequenceVectors<T extends SequenceElement>
extends WordVectorsImpl<T>
implements WordVectors
    SequenceVectors implements abstract features extraction for Sequences and SequenceElements, using SkipGram, CBOW or DBOW (for Sequence features extraction).
